Summary Method for an Object of Class ctmedmc

Source: R/cTMed-methods.R
summary.ctmedmc.Rd

Summary Method for an Object of Class ctmedmc

Usage

# S3 method for ctmedmc
summary(object, alpha = 0.05, ...)

Arguments

object

Object of class ctmedmc.

alpha

Numeric vector. Significance level \(\alpha\).

...

additional arguments.

Value

Returns a matrix of effects, time-interval, estimates, standard errors, test statistics, p-values, and confidence intervals.

Author

Ivan Jacob Agaloos Pesigan

# Specific time-interval ----------------------------------------------------
mc <- MCMed(
  phi = phi,
  vcov_phi_vec = vcov_phi_vec,
  delta_t = 1,
  from = "x",
  to = "y",
  med = "m",
  R = 100L # use a large value for R in actual research
)
summary(mc)
